{
  "texts": [
    "To generate the metadata necessary for the 'Topic' generalization form (see Section 5 or Appendix C), we opted for a bottom-up approach.",
    "This involved first clustering the dataset into thousands of fine-grained events, before clustering the event clusters into overarching topics.",
    "To achieve this, we used a heavily modified variant of BERTopic (Grootendorst 2022) with a gte-large foot_15 (Li et al. 2023) backbone.",
    "After embedding an entire year of the dataset, we first reduce their dimensionality using mini-batched PCA, and whiten the data.",
    "We construct a vocabulary over all the documents, by aggregating mini-batches of vocabularies."
  ]
}